Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which could place it in the cs.LG (Machine Learning) category. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category. Finally, the paper involves the use of graphics techniques, which could place it in the cs.GR (Graphics) category.
